quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  25,1,Usikelelekile loWo Wathumela iFur’kân1 (yokwahlula phakathi kokulungileyo nokungalunganga) kwisiCaka saKhe (uMuhammad) khon’ukuze abe nguMlumkisi kwindalo (yonke)
  25,2,"Yena loWo ubukumkani bamazulu nomhlaba ibobaKhe, Ongazelanga nyana Engazanga waba nahlakani kubumkani baKhe. Odale into nganye Wayilinganisela ngomlinganiselo oyifaneleyo"
  25,3,"Kodwa bazithabathele thixo bambi ngaphandle kwaKhe abangadalanga nto, lo gama kwabona bedaliwe, bengenabo nobunjani ubungozi nenzuzo eziqwini zabo okanye amandla okwenza ukufa okanye ubomi novuko"
  25,4,"Kananjalo abo bangakholwayo bathi, “Le (‘Kur’ân) Ayinto yimbi ngaphandle kokuba bubuxoki yena uyiqambile, yaye abanye abantu bamncedisile kuyo.” (Batsho) besenza ubuxoki obuyintswela bulungisa"
  25,5,"Kananjalo bathi: “Ziintsomi zabantu bakudala azibhale phantsi, yaye (abalandeli bakhe) bazinikele kuye ekuseni nasemini.”"
  25,6,"Yithi (Muhammad), “Ityhilwe nguYe Owazi (zonke) iimfihlelo ezisemazulwini nasemhlabeni. Inene Yena nguMxoleli, uSozinceba.”"
  25,7,"Kananjalo bathi: “NguMthunywa onjani lo utya ukutya ahamba hambe ezimarikeni? Kutheni kungathunyelwa ngelosi kuye ukuze ibe nguMlumkisi kunye naye?”"
  25,8,"Kungenjalo (kutheni kungekho) vimba amnikiweyo (ovela emazulwini), ingaba mhlawumbi unaso isitiya (amana) ukudla kuso?” Kananjalo abangakholwayo bathi: “Nina (maMuslim) anilandeli nto ngaphandle kokulandela indoda ethakathiweyo"
  25,9,"Khawubone ke (Muhammad) izinto abakufanisa nazo; kodwa bona balahlekile, yaye angekhe bayifumane iNdlela"